          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "\\[ \\text{Prorated Value} = \\left(\\frac{\\text{Days from Start to Prorate Date}}{\\text{Total Days in Range}}\\right) \\times \\text{Total Value} \\] This logic ensures that the prorated value is proportional to the time elapsed within the specified period."
